data.description: Charming 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home located in a prime location close to keck park and the Monterey trails. The home features a stepdown livingroom with a grand fireplace and flawless original hardwood flooring in the bedrooms. The home exterior features a corner lot with large 2 car garage. Bath count is different than tax records, buyer to verify if important.
